   {
    "progressNarration": "[textBlack:傍晚的黑暗是诅咒降临的不安信号。]@[textBlack:“魔女”在城中漫步，]@[textBlack:将人们拖入黑暗。]",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-45"
   },
   {
    "progressNarration": "[textBlack:你知道希望在哪里吗？]",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-46",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-45"
   },
   {
    "progressNarration": "[textBlack:光明即希望，希望即愿望。]@[textBlack:少女向白色的神奇动物诉说愿望后，]@[textBlack:强大的希望化为光，]@[textBlack:少女便能获得照亮黑暗的力量。]",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-47",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-46"
   },
   {
    "progressNarration": "[textBlack:“魔法少女”……就是这样诞生的。]",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-48",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-47"
   },
   {
    "progressNarration": "[textBlack:然而，黑暗会吞噬光明。]",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-49",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-48"
   },
   {
    "progressNarration": "[textBlack:黑暗即绝望，是光明与希望的反面。]@[textBlack:“魔法少女”坐上驶向绝望的列车，]@[textBlack:在与“魔女”奋战的过程中，]@[textBlack:逐渐染上绝望的色彩。]",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-50",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-49"
   },
   {
    "progressNarration": "[textBlack:染上绝望之人终将坠入黑暗……]",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-51",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-50"
   },
   {
    "progressNarration": "[textBlack:曾经无比闪耀的生命“宝石”失去所有光辉之时，]@[textBlack:“魔法少女”便会化为“魔女”。]",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-52",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-51"
   },
   {
    "progressNarration": "[textBlack:骨碌骨碌骨碌骨碌，负向轮回。]@[textBlack:数百年，数千年。]@[textBlack:牺牲，周而复始。]",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-53",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-52"
   },
   {
    "progressNarration": "[textBlack:痛苦……悲伤……羞愧……]@[textBlack:不知死亡为何物，我感到羞愧。]",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-54",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-53"
   },
   {
    "progressNarration": "[textBlack:所以我要记录……]",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-55",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-54"
   },
   {
    "progressNarration": "[textBlack:哪怕只是一个字、两个字，]@[textBlack:我也要为了我们的光明，反抗命运……]",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-56",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-55"
   },
   {
    "progressNarration": "[textBlack:知道真相的人越多，]@[textBlack:我们就越能照亮魔法少女的前路。]",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-57",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_102101/vo_full_102101-8-56"
   },
